 sampled_kind_type_4 AS kt1,
 sampled_kind_type_4 AS kt2,
 sampled_movie_companies_4 AS mc1,
 sampled_movie_companies_4 AS mc2,
 sampled_movie_info_idx_4 AS mi_idx1,
 sampled_movie_info_idx_4 AS mi_idx2,
 sampled_title_4 AS t1,
 sampled_title_4 AS t2
 WHERE it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id 
AND t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id
AND kt1.id = t1.kind_id
AND cn1.id = mc1.company_id
AND t1.id = mc1.movie_id 
AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id
AND it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id
AND t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id
AND kt2.id = t2.kind_id
AND cn2.id = mc2.company_id
AND t2.id = mc2.movie_id
AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id
AND cn1.country_code = '[de]'
AND it1.info = 'rating'
AND it2.info = 'votes distribution'
AND kt1.kind IN ('episode', 'tv movie', 'video game', 'tv series', 'tv series')
AND kt2.kind IN ('movie', 'video game', 'episode', 'tv movie', 'movie')
AND mi_idx2.info < '0000111101'
AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2001 AND 2006;
